{"tid":496561,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大家覺得點先算愛一個人？","createTime":"2017-12-11T19:51:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T20:07:31.000Z","uid":92671,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c175b776663b7f51ce39b894e84b543a003644e6","tid":496561,"uid":92671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T19:51:54.000Z","msg":"愛一個人嘅時候會:<br />\n無時無刻都會掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如佢零晨仲係街擔心佢安危<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 瞓唔安<br />\n會為佢無條件負出，物質定心靈都好，都想比最好嘅佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買得起嘅就送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (前提佢唔係拜金港女)，周不時會花心思為佢準備小驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  見到佢開心就覺得係最大嘅回報<br />\n佢嘅缺點都覺得係優點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  會嬲佢唔落<br />\n<br />\n女仔係咪都會咁諗？<br />\n<br />\n利申:巴打<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">諗諗下覺得老豆老母都係咁對我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，不孝子淨係掛住女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"60f08436d683da8a4a140d8f9ac6737c688c158e","tid":496561,"uid":151728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T20:01:02.000Z","msg":"講咁多你都係想人貼篇潮文俾你姐"},{"pid":"9c48b0595d842d70c3a9624504e9daa02cf83f1e","tid":496561,"uid":92671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T20:04:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講咁多你都係想人貼篇潮文俾你姐</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 資歷淺，請問邊一篇潮文符合主題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67de8fd93c7e9d317ece7e13bba7c68a4955c257","tid":496561,"uid":151728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T20:06:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講咁多你都係想人貼篇潮文俾你姐</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/